</p>

<p><asp:Label ID="Label1" runat="server" 
    Text="Collection of Information" 
    SkinID="labelTitleColor1_Medium" /></p>

<p>Our Site has an optional case study download and an optional contact form, which require a User to give us contact information (e.g., User's name, phone number and email address), demographic information (e.g., User's city, state and zip code) and professional information (e.g., User's company name and title). We use this contact information to respond to the User's comments, to contact the User when necessary, or send the User information about our company, services or other related information. We do not sell or disseminate such contact information to anyone outside our company except as explained below. Users may opt-out of receiving calls or emails from us by notifying us in accordance with the choice/opt-out section below.</p>

<p>Our Site also provides the ability to log-in to our ServiceCOMMAND ticket tracking service.  Whether you place your service call request over the phone or via the internet, Scantron Technology Solutions' ServiceCOMMAND offers you the ability to track your call from placement to completion, to view tickets' statuses, and to register for auto-email notifications.</p>

<p>Our Site's registration form for ServiceCOMMAND requires the User to give us contact information (e.g., User's name, phone number and email address).  The User's contact information is used to contact such User when necessary. We do not sell or disseminate such contact information to anyone outside our company except as explained below.  Users may opt-out of receiving calls or emails from us by notifying us in accordance with the choice/opt-out section below.</p>

<p>We also use cookies for those logged in to our ServiceCOMMAND ticket tracking service in order to confirm authentication and authorization during active sessions. We do not persistently store information on a User's device.  We use a User's IP address to help diagnose problems with our server and to administer the Site.  A User's IP address is also used to monitor levels of activity and to gather broad demographic information.</p>

<p><asp:Label ID="Label2" runat="server" 
    Text="Disclosure to Third Parties" 
    SkinID="labelTitleColor1_Medium" /></p>

<p>We will not disclose any User contact information to third parties except to:</p>
<ul class="ulDefault">
    <li>Affiliated companies (e.g., subsidiaries and other companies owned by or controlled by Harland Clarke Holdings Corporation) who may only use the information for the purposes described above.</li>
    <li>Our service providers that provide services for us such as sending emails on our behalf and processing payments.</li>
    <li>Effect a merger, acquisition, or otherwise; to support the sale or transfer of business assets; to enforce our rights or protect our property; to protect the rights, property or safety of others, investigate fraud, respond to a government request; or as needed to support auditing, compliance and corporate governance functions. </li>
</ul>

<p><asp:Label ID="Label3" runat="server" 
