<p>Scantron Technology Solutions is headquartered in the United States of America. Information may be accessed by us or transferred to us in the United States or to our affiliates or service providers elsewhere in the world. By providing us with information, you consent to this transfer. We will protect the privacy and security of this information according to this Privacy Statement, regardless of where it is processed or stored.</p>

<p><asp:Label ID="Label6" runat="server" 
    Text="Changes to this Privacy Statement" 
    SkinID="labelTitleColor1_Medium" /></p>

<p>From time to time, we may update this Privacy Statement to clarify our practices or to reflect new or different privacy practices, such as when we add new features to our Site.  If we make any material changes we will notify you by email (sent to the email address specified in your ServiceCOMMAND account) or by means of notice on the Site prior to the change becoming effective. We encourage you to periodically review this page for the latest information about our privacy practices.</p>

