<p>Users can opt-out of receiving communications from us, request to have us remove their information from our databases and/or no longer receive our services by sending an email to hts.marketing@scantronts.com with OPT-OUT in the subject (Please specify the contact type to prohibit in the message) or by calling us at (800) 228-3628 extension 3114.</p>

